---
title: Seared Sweet Italian Sausage with Warm Orzo Salad
description: Orzo pasta is perfect for soups and salads. In this warm salad, sausage serves as the ultimate flavor bomb, and carrots, zucchini and bell peppers create a fresh and colorful presentation. We finished it with a fresh squeeze of lemon to brighten the flavors.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54d221906ced6e7e1b8b4567.jpg
